rows.label: bf02160100_0010
rows.name: They're...so strong!

rows.label: bf02160100_0015
rows.name:
Such strength from a measly two fighters...
They're Drivers, all right!

rows.label: bf02160100_0020
rows.name: Rex! Now!

rows.label: bf02160100_0030
rows.name: You got it!

rows.label: bf02160100_0040
rows.name: Wha-?! A wall made of fire?!

rows.label: bf02160100_0050
rows.name: Such a commotion.

rows.label: bf02160100_0052
rows.name:
Just when I thought I could enjoy a little
peace and quiet.

rows.label: bf02160100_0060
rows.name: K-Kagutsuchi-sama!

rows.label: bf02160100_0070
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi?
Is she a Blade? Wh-where's her Driver?

rows.label: bf02160100_0080
rows.name:
My Driver is otherwise engaged at present.
I am here alone.

rows.label: bf02160100_0090
rows.name: No...Driver?

rows.label: bf02160100_0100
rows.name: Ba ha ha!

rows.label: bf02160100_0110
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi-sama is the "Jewel of Superbia"!
The strongest Blade in the Empire!

rows.label: bf02160100_0120
rows.name: Even alone, she's more than a match for you!

rows.label: bf02160100_0130
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi-sama, these miscreants are
terrorists working for Iira.

rows.label: bf02160100_0140
rows.name: Please lend me your power to bring them to justice!

rows.label: bf02160100_0150
rows.name: Iira?

rows.label: bf02160100_0160
rows.name:
That emerald Core Crystal...
Could it really be true?

rows.label: bf02160100_0170
rows.name: Well, well.

rows.label: bf02160100_0180
rows.name:
Captain Pax, you are not to kill them.
Take these ones in alive.

rows.label: bf02160100_0190
rows.name: Hey, get that thing!

rows.label: bf02160100_0200
rows.name: Roger!
